# Responsive Navigation Menu Project

A responsive navigation menu with fixed position, interactive scroll and hover effects.

## Features

- Fixed, responsive navbar
- Color/style changes on scroll and link hover
- Modern layout and clean code separation

## Usage

1. Download all files (`index.html`, `styles.css`, `script.js`, `README.md`) into one folder.
2. Open `index.html` in your browser.

## Customization

- Update navigation links and content in `index.html`.
- Change colors and spacing in `styles.css` to fit your theme.
- Footer text can be edited in the HTML file.

---

**Open source. Feel free to use and modify!**
